{"tid":681489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大角嘴男子遭妻斬手 負傷走50米浴血街頭","createTime":"2018-05-28T05:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T17:12:04.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"527da798d29044374402a69cca5bc28a7b37e563","tid":681489,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:49:38.000Z","msg":"【狠妻斬夫】【天眼直擊】大角嘴男子遭妻斬手 負傷走50米浴血街頭<br />\n<br />\n【12:36】新增cctv片段<br />\n<br />\n大角嘴大全街47號一間餐廳，早上9時34分，一名男侍應在餐廳工作期間，其妻前來找他，兩人走出店外傾談，其間疑因感情問題發生爭執，愈吵愈烈，妻子突以利刀襲擊男事主，男事主被斬傷手部，他負傷由大全街往大角嘴道方向逃走，右轉入大政街再橫過埃華街，走了約50米，最後不支倒地，地面遺下一條血路，有救護車剛經過現場，發現男傷者手部淌血，立即停車施救，再將他送伊利沙白醫院治理。妻子逞兇後逃去，警方正調查事件，以及追緝涉案女子。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》獲得事發後一條cctv片段顯示，穿著圍裙的男侍應事主，左手滿手鮮血，一臉驚慌地沿大全街逃跑，懷疑是其長髮披肩的妻子，則手持大袋追在他身後，估計男傷者跑得太快，其妻未有追及，稍後橫過馬路後逃去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180528/58246281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F58246281&d=jVfVKlZMpNPP2cvnjC5RPu9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=5aa4a253\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180528%2F58246281&h=69e49bfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180528/58246281</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/t_original/omswuashicihys0tphzf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kinja-img.com%2Fgawker-media%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Ft_original%2Fomswuashicihys0tphzf.gif&h=f8936fcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b36442af99151d27d8a3548578bf8003cae2d54","tid":681489,"uid":187909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:51:07.000Z","msg":"賭撚？"},{"pid":"2b4ae0966215683469cc65000820f9abd7781530","tid":681489,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T05:52:24.000Z","msg":"仁王<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" cla